      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/16/7",
      "text": [
        " : قُلْتُ لَهُ إِنَّ جَمَّالاً لَنَا كَانَ يُكَارِينَا فَحَمَلَ عَلَى غَيْرِهِ فَضَاعَ قَالَ \"ضَمِّنْهُ وَ خُذْ مِنْهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3926 - Uthman bin Ziyad narrated from Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), who said:\nI said to Imam (as): \"We had a camel driver who used to work for us. He loaded goods onto someone else's camel, and they were lost.\"\nImam (as) said: \"Hold him liable and take compensation from him.\""
        ]
      }
    },
